r|The Visitor (2007 drama film)}}''\n| 2008\n| Professor Walter Vale\n| [[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]]\n| {{ubl|[[Boston Society of Film Critics Award for Best Actor]] {{small|(3rd place)}}|[[Boston Society of Film Critics Award for Best Cast]] {{small|(2nd place)}}|[[Method Fest Independent Film Festival|Method Fest Independent Film Festival for Best Actor]]|[[30th Moscow International Film Festival|Moscow International Film Festival for Best Actor]]<ref name=\"Moscow2008\">{{cite web |url=http://www.moscowfilmfestival.ru/miff34/eng/archives/?year=2008 |title=30th Moscow International Film Festival (2008) |accessdate=2013-06-02 |work=MIFF |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421050837/http://www.moscowfilmfestival.ru/miff34/eng/archives/?year=2008 |archivedate=2013-04-21 }}</ref>|[[National Board of Review|National Board of Review \u2014 Spotlight Award]]|[[San Diego Film Critics Society]] \u2014 Special Award|[[Santa Barbara International Film Festival|Santa Barbara International Film Festival \u2014 Virtuoso Award]]|[[Satellite Award for Best Actor \u2013 Motion Picture]]|Nominated\u2014[[Academy Award for Best Actor]]|Nominated\u2014[[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Actor|Broadcast Film Critics Association Award for Best Actor]]|Nominated\u2014[[Chicago Film Critics Association Award for Best Actor]]|Nominated\u2014[[Dallas\u2013Fort Worth Film Critics Association Award for Best Actor]]|Nominated\u2014[[Gotham Independent Film Award for Best Ensemble Cast]]|Nominated\u2014[[Independent Spirit Award for Best Male Lead]]|Nominated\u2014[[Online Film Critics Society Award for Best Actor]]|Nominated\u2014[[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Leading Role]]}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''{{sortname|The|Broken|The Broken (film)}}''\n| 2008\n| John McVey\n| [[Sean Ellis]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Step Brothers (film)|Step Brothers]]''\n| 2008\n| Dr. Robert Doback\n| [[Adam McKay]]\n| [[San Diego Film Critics Society]] \u2014 Special Award\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Burn After Reading]]''\n| 2008\n| Ted Treffon\n| [[Coen brothers|Joel Coen<br>Ethan Coen]]\n| [[San Diego Film Critics Society]] \u2014 Special Award\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''{{sortname|The|Tale of Despereaux|The Tale of Despereaux (film)}}''\n| 2008\n| Principal\n| [[Sam Fell]]<br/>Robert Stevenhagen\n| Voice<br>[[San Diego Film Critics Society]] \u2014 Special Award\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Waiting for Forever]]''\n| 2009\n| Richard Twist\n| [[James Keach]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[happythankyoumoreplease]]''\n| 2010\n| Paul Gertmanian \n| [[Josh Radnor]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Dear John (2010 film)|Dear John]]''\n| 2010\n| Bill Tyree\n| [[Lasse Hallstr\u00f6m]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Eat Pray Love]]''\n| 2010\n| Richard\n| [[Ryan Murphy (writer)|Ryan Murphy]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Norman (film)|Norman]]''\n| 2010\n| Doug Long\n| [[Jonathan Segal]]\n| Breckenridge Festival of Film for Best Ensemble Cast\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Let Me In (film)|Let Me In]]''\n| 2010\n| The Father\n| [[Matt Reeves]]\n| [[Fangoria|Fangoria Chainsaw Awards for Best Supporting Actor]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Friends with Benefits (film)|Friends with Benefits]]''\n| 2011\n| Mr. Harper\n| [[Will Gluck]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''{{sortname|The|Rum Diary|The Rum Diary (film)}}''\n| 2011\n| Edward J. Lotterman\n| [[Bruce Robinson]]\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Hall Pass]]''\n| 2011\n| Coakley\n| [[Farrelly brothers|Peter Farrelly<br>Bobby Farrelly]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Liberal Arts (film)|Liberal Arts]]''\n| 2012\n| Professor Peter Hoberg \n| [[Josh Radnor]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Darling Companion]]''\n| 2012\n| Russell\n| [[Lawrence Kasdan]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''{{sortname|The|Cabin in the Woods}}''\n| 2012\n| Gary Sitterson <!-- Richard is not said and Novel says Gary -->\n| [[Drew Goddard]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Killing Them Softly]]''\n| 2012\n| Driver\n| [[Andrew Dominik]]\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Jack Reacher (film)|Jack Reacher]]''\n| 2012\n| Alex Rodin\n| [[Christopher McQuarrie]]\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Company You Keep (film)|The Company You Keep]]''\n| 2012\n| Jed Lewis\n| [[Robert Redford]]\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[White House Down]]''\n| 2013\n| [[Speaker of the United States House of Representatives|Speaker]] Eli Raphelson\n| [[Roland Emmerich]]\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Turbo (film)|Turbo]]''\n| 2013\n| Bobby\n| [[David Soren (animator)|David Soren]]\n| Voice \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[A.C.O.D.]]''\n| 2013\n| Hugh\n| Stu Zicherman\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[God's Pocket]]''\n| 2014\n| Richard Shelburn\n| [[John Slattery]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[4 Minute Mile]]''\n| 2014\n| Coach Coleman\n| [[Charles-Olivier Michaud]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Lullaby (2014 film)|Lullaby]]''\n| 2014\n| Robert\n| [[Andrew Levitas]]\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Bone Tomahawk]]''\n| 2015\n| Chicory\n| [[S. Craig Zahler]]\n| Nominated\u2014[[Independent Spirit Award for Best Supporting Male]] \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]''\n| 2015\n| [[Richard Sipe]]\n| [[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]]\n| Uncredited voice cameo\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Hollars]]''\n| 2016\n| Don Hollar\n| [[John Krasinski]]\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[LBJ (film)|LBJ]]''\n| 2016\n| Senator [[Richard Russell Jr.|Richard Russell]]\n| [[Rob Reiner]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kong: Skull Island]]''\n| 2017\n| Senator Al Willis\n| [[Jordan Vogt-Roberts]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Shape of Water]]''\n| 2017\n| Giles\n| [[Guillermo del Toro]]\n|[[St. Louis Gateway Film Critics Association Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br/>[[Online Film Critics Society Award for Best Supporting Actor]] <small>(2nd place)</small><br/>[[Dallas\u2013Fort Worth Film Critics Association Award for Best Actor]] <small>(3rd place)</small><br/>Nominated\u2014[[Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br/>Nominated\u2014[[Austin Film Critics Association Awards 2017|Austin Film Critics Association Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br/>Nominated\u2014[[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br/>Nominated\u2014[[Detroit Film Critics Society Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br/>Nominated\u2014[[Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Motion Picture]]<br/>Nominated\u2014San Francisco Film Critics Circle Award for Best Supporting Actor<br />Nominated\u2014[[Houston Film Critics Society Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br/>Nominated\u2014[[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Supporting Role]]<br/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Kajillionaire]]''\n| 2020\n| Robert\n| [[Miranda July]]\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Last Shift]]''\n| 2020\n| Stanley\n| [[Andrew Cohn]]\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Humans (film)|The Humans]]''\n| TBA\n| Erik Blake\n| [[Stephen Karam]]\n| Post-production\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Nightmare Alley (upcoming film)|Nightmare Alley]]''\n| TBA\n| Ezra Grindle\n|[[Guillermo del Toro]]\n| Filming\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Great Performances]]''\n| 1974, 1975\n| Warder / The Sheriff\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[American Playhouse]]''\n| 1984\n| Nicholas Vazzana\n| Episode: \"Concealed Enemies, Part I: Suspicion\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Spenser: For Hire]]''\n| 1985\n| Tex\n| Episode: \"Internal Affairs\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Miami Vice]]''\n| 1985, 1989\n| Goodman / DEA Agent Ed Waters\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''The Little Sister''\n| 1986\n| Roger Davis \n| Television film\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[In the Line of Duty: The F.B.I. Murders]]''\n| 1988\n| Detective\n| [[Television film]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Out on th